| [handleUpload(file)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#452-509) | Uploads PDF with `chat_id`, updates status |
| [sendQuestion()](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#527-563) | Posts question with `chat_id`, displays response |
| [addMessage(role, text)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#567-588) | Renders a chat bubble in the DOM |

